{"type": "article", "id": 24299, "title": "平衡灯2", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-23T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140301oDhElwmGW4b0AO7g.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组落地灯来自中国设计团队 yuue，圆形灯头和大理石底座之间是一个类似三角形的结构，灯头所在的铁杆通过弧形的杠杆上下摆动，可以看到天平秤和跷跷板的影子。灯头和杠杆结构也恰成点和线的关系，保持了几何图形的简洁美感。平衡灯 2 是他们之间的升级版，有黑白两款，预计今年上市，<a href=\"http://www.yuue-design.com/works_zh/balancer_zh/\">这里是工作室主页。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140259oJj6WhcNqT4xkGQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140259Q7M0cqXRwNynCZlV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140300WfcsGTmN9wJPp6B0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140300uV5WaJ3OzYX8PGyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}